<strong>Advisor Robe - AC 8</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/advisor_robe.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/chest.shtml">Chest</a><BR>
Weight: 3.5 - DEF, ERU, GNM, HEF, HIE, HUM, IKS<BR>
Classes: <a href="/enchanter/armour/chest.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/chest.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/chest.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/chest.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/chest.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(AGI +2) (INT +5) (Sv Magic +5) (Mana +20) </font>
<BR>
Found in mistmoore.<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 3643pp (38 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 2792pp (13 quotes)<BR>

