<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Me..</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-22 07:19:23</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Seeing as how this is a new item, and I was one of the first people to see it drop on my server, I figure I'll post some info. This is a great upgrade to an FBR, and some may prefer it to an Oracle Robe itself, due to the save vs magic on it. The robe drops off of a level 40ish DE Wizard, by the name of The Advisor, who is found near the library in the castle in side Mistmoore. Wouldn't be hard to kill solo, but hard to get to due to all the mobs near him that will agro quite nicely. If you're going to check this out invis, watch the undead mobs, who will see through it. Basically looks like Robe of the Ishva only red. First person to get it on Lanys T'vyl was Luran, after two deaths, no less. =P<BR>
/cheer Luran<BR>
<BR>
Darwinain Seafarer<BR>
25th Cleric<BR>
Gyn Cadley Reejeryn<BR>
Lanys T'vyl</font></td></tr></table>
